    "description": "adish Co., Ltd. provides growth and adoption support solutions in Japan. The company offers growth support services for startups comprising CS Studio that provides customer success, consultation, and office-based/temporary help services; Start-up Growth Support with agile operational structure to deal with issues, such as responding to a surge in inquiries, setting communication preferences, and troubleshooting; and Internet Monitoring that provides monitoring services for appropriate postings. It also provides Adoption Support Services to business companies and educational institutions, including School Guardian, which provides support for personal information leakage on the internet and cyber bullying; Pazu for in-house measurement against flaming and social media literacy; hitobo for streamlining business operations with AL chatbot; matte, an AI alert function; and Front Support, an operational service for social media fan community. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
